<plot>A documentary filmmaker conducts a series of interviewers with Molly, a pick pocket disguised as a college student. Over the course of these encounters, the filmmaker's intentions are revealed to be less than perfect and Molly begins to question why she is participating in the project. The conflict between the two culminates in Molly quitting the movie, forcing the filmmaker to use his raw footage as the finished product.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?012271</url></doc>
